{"tid":1737465,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既「黃金精神」","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T13:46:12.000Z","uid":12633,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c31b5b730d6afc6aad56d844b0fe9fffd114d5b","tid":1737465,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"話說JoJo 第五季結尾有一個小故事，好似尋日既香港：<br />\n<br />\n命運注定男主角 阿布 將會死亡，而佢既隊友用盡一切辦法想去改變呢個命運，要去拯救 阿布。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4oAZZks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4oAZZks.png&h=d0d299b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMTdjkv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMTdjkv.png&h=4419257f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHtHW7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHtHW7d.png&h=f90b4b94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPETjkB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPETjkB.png&h=5ff6e025&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TvrEkD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TvrEkD.png&h=50ec50e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUL3Gy0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUL3Gy0.png&h=9491e13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般人認為「命運」無法抵抗，為左過得輕鬆啲，所以坦然接受「命運」。<br />\n<br />\n而故事既最後，隊友們為左拯救 阿布，白白犧牲左三名手足，而 阿布 亦逃不過死亡既「命運」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJAnW8M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJAnW8M.png&h=c357996a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wE7mtfs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwE7mtfs.png&h=0ed6c8f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioXhL2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioXhL2a.png&h=6b4b3714&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2w6Enc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2w6Enc.png&h=fed31166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">命運無改變到，反而犧牲左更多人，咁點解我地要嘗試去改變呢個命運？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKMZeVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKMZeVW.png&h=b9d13af9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dd9jZnE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDd9jZnE.png&h=de6d36f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfGB1A2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfGB1A2.png&h=829c37ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2GFJRa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2GFJRa.jpg&h=44faa64f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5a6764080a31f59a1748665f97f8be0a57753fb","tid":1737465,"uid":12633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWWB1C1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWWB1C1.jpg&h=08ac1c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4631th2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4631th2.jpg&h=15fa6ff3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6faea64ce39e6986a08a9451a6245a3afa1c0102","tid":1737465,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3abd8c9f7ecf21000ac518fa314ae167e9c7693","tid":1737465,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132aab1b44d948daf918a0529a2c9c12f8b56e4b","tid":1737465,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=